2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=7515f5f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwong.w.ming</a><br />\n我諗以上人士都應該唔想去美國，佢哋申請美國簽證申請應該凍過水，因為我懷疑以上人渣係 圈中人 嘅startup戶口群嚟。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 陳澍唔交代都唔緊要，呢單嘢夠晒料證明Facebook Hong Kong and Taiwan同共產黨關係密切，我認為台灣政府同美國政府係時候對Facebook採取行動，甚至應該引用國家安全法律搜查Facecook Server同辦公室，喺我眼中，Zuckerberg真係同賣國賊無分別。<br />\n<br />\n圈中人係乜水，我等Facebook交代清楚，定有公司會刪咗個Page。<br />\n<br />\n(個Page係我用正常Facebook Search搵唔到，我要掃系統先Search，仲要Facebook詭異地block咗我大數據系統嘅data feed，有啲人做緊仆街嘢都好明顯，係Facebook公司全力配合)<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/27161/%e5%9c%88%e4%b8%ad%e4%ba%ba-%e7%99%bb%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e5%98%85%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e9%82%8a%e5%ba%a6%e5%9a%9f%ef%bc%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F27161%2F%25e5%259c%2588%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e4%25ba%25ba-%25e7%2599%25bb%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%2591%258a%25e5%2598%2585%25e8%25b3%2587%25e9%2587%2591%25e9%2582%258a%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e5%259a%259f%25ef%25bc%259f&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8uvhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=bc819473\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/27161/%e5%9c%88%e4%b8%ad%e4%ba%ba-%e7%99%bb%e5%bb%a3%e5%91%8a%e5%98%85%e8%b3%87%e9%87%91%e9%82%8a%e5%ba%a6%e5%9a%9f%ef%bc%9f</a>"},{"pid":"27640e2bdcd9160c542d159bdfcca1e8f36ec8d6","tid":1190864,"uid":226656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3c08782f526bca41a4cf1289b2d9b6e8063c92","tid":1190864,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:23:03.000Z","msg":"樓主做fb?"},{"pid":"19c6f844e976f9b28658b60dcda92c5fa3e1adfb","tid":1190864,"uid":65879,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T21:26:51.000Z","msg":"N年前得罪左個台灣律師<br />\n第二日login facebook<br />\n佢話我個account俾人係台灣法院登入過<br />\nFacebook安全？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47f17b5d5e83ffe5f4